#- Martini§0
§0
§02.5oz Gin§0
§00.5oz Vermouth§0
§0Garnish: 1 or 3 olives or lemon twist§0
§0
§0Fill Cocktail Shaker§0
§0Shake§0
§0Strain and Pour into Martini Glass§0
§0Garnish§0
§0Enjoy!
#- Death in the Afternoon§0
§0
§0~1.5oz Absinthe§0
§0~4.5oz Champagne§0
§0
§0Pour one jigger absinthe into a Champagne glass. Add iced champagne until it attains the proper opalescent milkiness. Drink three to five of these slowly
#- Whiskey Moon§0
§08oz Blue Moon§0
§01.5 oz Whiskey§0
§03/4oz Lemon Juice§0
§01/4oz Simple Syrup§0
§0Garnish: Orange Peel§0
§0  Maraschino Cherry§0
§0Fill Cocktail Shaker, §0
§0Shake and Strain into double old fashioned glass, top with Blue Moon, Garnish and serve. Enjoy!
#- Sidecar§0
§0
§02oz Cognac or Brandy§0
§01oz Cointreau§0
§03/4oz lemon juice§0
§0
§0Combine Brandy, Cointreau, and lemon juice in cocktail shaker, Shake well, strain into glass, garnish with lemon peel or orange peel. 
#- Brandy Alexander§0
§0
§01 Part Cognac§0
§01 Part Creme de cacao§0
§01 Part Fresh Cream§0
§0
§0Shake and strain into a chilled cocktail glass§0
§0Sprinkle with fresh ground nutmeg.
