#- Gin and Tonic§0
§0
§03oz Gin§0
§04oz Tonic Water§0
§01tbsp fresh lime juice§0
§0Garnish: Lime Wedge§0
§0
§0Place ice in tall glass§0
§0add Gin, tonic water, and lime juice, Stir Well Garnish with lime wedge§0
§0
§0Cures Malaria
#- Margarita§0
§0
§07 parts Tequila§0
§04 parts Cointreau§0
§03 parts lime juice§0
§0
§0Pour all ingredients into shaker with ice. §0
§0Shake well and strain into cocktail glass rimmed with salt.§0
§0
§0Fresh Lime Juice is Key
#- Screwdriver§0
§0
§01 part Vodka§0
§02 parts Orange Juice§0
§0
§0Mix in a highball glass with ice. Garnish with an orange slice and serve on the rocks.§0
§0
§0Timing: All Day
#- Dark and Stormy§0
§0
§03 parts dark rum§0
§05 parts ginger beer§0
§0
§0Fill glass with ice, add rum and top with ginger beer. Garnish with lime wedge. Served in a highball glass.§0
§0
§0Enjoy on a Rainy Day
